                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-19-off91 t18000917-19-cd92"></join>, ten china cups, value 4s. and a tea-pot, value 1s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18000917-19-victim214" type="victimName">
                  Benjamin 
                  Powers
